skill_constraints: Significant DevOps and Accessibility skill gaps.
resource_bottlenecks: Backend Lead for architecture decisions; Frontend Lead for accessibility.
mitigation_strategies: Heavy reliance on individual expertise; risk of burnout.

skill_constraints: DevOps skill gap mitigated by contractor.
resource_bottlenecks: Accessibility implementation still relies heavily on Frontend Lead.
mitigation_strategies: Contractor handles all infrastructure, freeing up backend team. Pair programming for accessibility.

scenario_name: Reduced Team (4 FTE - Loss of 1 Senior)
skill_constraints: Loss of a senior creates a major skill gap and single point of failure.
resource_bottlenecks: All remaining senior resources are overloaded.
mitigation_strategies: De-scope non-critical features (e.g., Google Sheets integration, some reports).
